The Skyway is a heavenly dimension 
located high in the sky. The Skyway 
bears a striking resemblance to 
[[[aether| The Aether]]], containing the 
same mobs, biomes and structures. The 
primary difference between the Skyway 
and the Aether, is the coordinate scale.

Similarly to [[[nether| The Nether]]], travel 
within the Skyway is significantly more 
efficient than in the Overworld, with each 
block in the Skyway corresponding to ten 
blocks in the Overworld. This 
increased travel speed, combined with the 
ability to fall through the void and emerge 
at the top of the Overworld, is what gives 
the Skyway its name.
[[/div]]

